<section xml:id="quiz-9">

    <title>Week 9 Quiz</title>
    <!--<title>Week 9 Qui<m>\scalebox{-1}[1]{z}</m></title>
    <plaintitle>Week 9 Quiz</plaintitle>-->

    <p>Suppose that <m>f \in \sR[0,1]</m>. Compute 
        <md>
            <mrow  number="yes" xml:id="limit-integral9"> \lim_{n \to \iy} \int_0^1 f(x) x^n \dx </mrow>
        </md>.
    </p>

    <p>
        Note that this is the same as in <xref ref="limit-integral9"/>
    </p>

</section>
